ActOld Age Security Act
SubjectComing into Force of the Canada-Republic of Austria Agreement on Social Security
PrecisOrder declaring that AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY BETWEEN CANADA AND THE REPUBLIC OF AUSTRIA enters into force on the first day of the fourth month after each Party has notified the other by diplomatic note that it has completed the internal legal procedures necessary for the entry into force of this Agreement.
